snippet.title: Headcrab Frenzy! Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Headcrab Frenzy is a free dynamic action Half-Life mod which allows you to quench a desire to destroy these little bouncy critters to your heart's content, hold records, get achievements, and try your hand at cooperative gameplay, competing in public statistics.

http://store.steampowered.com/app/354900
